his heirs mark antony and octavian confronted the assassins of caesar , marcus junius brutus and gaius cassius longinus , at the battle of philippi on the plain to the west of the city during october in 42 bc. antony and octavian were victorious in this final battle against the partisans of the republic .

he died a deadly death : after the second battle of philippi in 42 b.c. , this roman general could have said , " et tu , me ? " as he killed himself

